{"tid":2374014,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人有咁嘅狀況？","createTime":"2021-01-21T02:05:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T10:06:33.000Z","uid":154060,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8a1b585e146c4ac1ac1525fac17d086744fa903b","tid":2374014,"uid":154060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T02:05:58.000Z","msg":"1. 易燥底<br />\n一件事情如果有少少唔順利 個人就會開始燥底<br />\n輕則黑面 重則會燥身邊嘅人 （即使係唔關事）<br />\n<br />\n2. 怨天但不尤人<br />\n覺得自己身邊嘅環境因素好差 會問點解人地咁好 自己就出生係D咁嘅家庭 <br />\n<br />\n3. 好陰謀論 <br />\n成日覺得人地有野瞞佢 諗到件事好複雜 唔相信人地做緊嘅野 佢覺得佢得出嚟嘅就係事實 <br />\n<br />\n4. 會企係高地度人身攻擊 <br />\n由基本高矮肥瘦到去外國讀書係買學位 多材多藝係因為屋企有錢等等（駁唔到）<br />\n<br />\n長期諗野都好負面 所有野都向壞方向諗 之後就開始「自己嘅世界」 有無人都有咁嘅狀況？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb92bca83116a53b7f27403db2fb01576892ca30","tid":2374014,"uid":137275,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T02:26:34.000Z","msg":"你係女？"},{"pid":"8c256fd95ec5728fa46f6ef64e447d79aeae3fd2","tid":2374014,"uid":154060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb92bca83116a53b7f27403db2fb01576892ca30","tid":2374014,"uid":137275,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T02:26:34.000Z","msg":"你係女？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T06:52:23.000Z","msg":"仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b1d31083e8234079028a4394fa6540d70e5d098","tid":2374014,"uid":142094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T07:35:27.000Z","msg":"Me<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 全中"},{"pid":"f3901d22f9be10731b899866cc8e636c65178cf4","tid":2374014,"uid":186374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T08:35:55.000Z","msg":"好簡單<br />\n因為你對現狀不滿<br />\n對自己又不滿<br />\n自尊感低"},{"pid":"a19f4d8d7bedc221929181db91f719c2609af5fc","tid":2374014,"uid":154060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b1d31083e8234079028a4394fa6540d70e5d098","tid